  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个抢答游戏的流程图，从每轮开始讲起。首先是一个起点，叫\"Start of Round\"，然后家庭成员按下抢答器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start of Round",
        "Family Member Buzzes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点之后接一个判断节点，问是否有家庭成员抢答。那如果第一个抢答的人，我们怎么表示？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Family Member Buzzes",
        "First to Buzz"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，从抢答判断分出两条路：如果是第一个抢答的，进入\"First to Buzz\"状态，然后这个人要回答。如果不是第一个，那就把机会给另一组的家庭成员。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First to Buzz",
        "Answers",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以\"First to Buzz\"是个菱形判断，Yes分支到\"Answers\"，No分支到\"Chance to Other Family's Member\"。接下来回答之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "First to Buzz",
        "Answers",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "回答之后要验证答案，我称之为\"Is Response on Board?\"，就是答案是否在答题板上。这个验证很关键，我想把它放在一个子图里，叫\"RoundStart\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Is Response on Board?",
        "RoundStart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加子图RoundStart，里面包含答案验证节点。如果答案在板上，下一步要做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RoundStart",
        "Is Response on Board?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果Yes，要\"Check if Answer is Highest\"，检查这个答案是不是最高分。如果是最高分，这家人继续答题；如果不是，机会转给另一家人。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if Answer is Highest",
        "Family Continues Answering",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，CompareAnswer节点分出Yes到FamilyContinues，No回到OtherFamilyChance。那如果答案根本不在板上呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if Answer is Highest",
        "Family Continues Answering",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "答案不在板上，直接判错，同样走\"Chance to Other Family's Member\"。所以CheckResponse的No分支也指向OtherFamilyChance。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Is Response on Board?",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "RoundStart子图已完成。现在处理另一家人抢答的情况，这部分也需要一个子图吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RoundStart",
        "OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，叫\"OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart\"。另一家的成员回答后，同样要验证\"Is New Response on Board?\"，注意这里用New区分一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart",
        "Answers",
        "Is New Response on Board?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，OtherFamilyChance指向OtherMemberAnswers，然后到CheckNewResponse。如果新答案在板上，走Yes分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Chance to Other Family's Member",
        "Answers",
        "Is New Response on Board?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Yes分支到\"Check if New Answer is Higher\"，检查新答案是否更高分。如果更高，\"New Family Continues Answering\"；如果不高，回到原来的\"Family Continues Answering\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if New Answer is Higher",
        "New Family Continues Answering",
        "Family Continues Answering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "CompareNewAnswer的Yes到NewFamilyContinues，No回到FamilyContinues。那如果新答案根本不在板上呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if New Answer is Higher",
        "New Family Continues Answering",
        "Family Continues Answering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果不在板上，进入\"Next 2 Family Members to Buzz\"，就是下一轮抢答，让剩下的两个家庭成员继续抢。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Is New Response on Board?",
        "Next 2 Family Members to Buzz"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart子图已添加完成。我检查一下整体结构，发现CompareAnswer的No分支和CheckResponse的No分支都指向OtherFamilyChance，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if Answer is Highest",
        "Is Response on Board?",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，两种失败情况都归到同一出口。另外CompareNewAnswer的No分支要回到FamilyContinues，这个别忘了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if New Answer is Higher",
        "Family Continues Answering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个细节想确认：CompareNewAnswer的No分支是回到FamilyContinues，而不是OtherFamilyChance，这样设计的原因是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if New Answer is Higher",
        "Family Continues Answering",
        "Chance to Other Family's Member"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "因为新答案虽然有效但分数不高，说明原来那家人的答案更好，所以控制权还给他们。只有答案无效或者没有答案时，才需要换机会。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check if New Answer is Higher",
        "Family Continues Answering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
