      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，逻辑很清晰。我再核对一下所有节点名称：Start of Round、Family Member Buzzes、First to Buzz、Answers、Chance to Other Family's Member，还有子图内的各个节点。",
